{"word":"ἄκραντος","slug":"ἄκραντος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἄκραντος</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:κραίνω'><el>κραίνω</el></a>, like epic <a href='S:ἀκράαντος'><el>ἀκράαντος</el></a>\n<p/><i>unfulfilled, fruitless</i>, <b><a href='S:Pindar'>Pind.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>:—<a href='S:neuter'>neut.</a> <a href='S:plural'>pl.</a> as <a href='S:Adverb'>adv.</a>, <i>in vain</i>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/>"}]}